MATHEMATICAL  FORMULATION  
The  hydrogenic  narrative  wavefunction:  
\Psi_{life}(t)  =  \sum_{i=1}^{N}  w_i  \cdot  \Psi(H_n,  A_m,  S_k,  E_j)  
Where:  
●  H_n  =  hydrogen  state  
 ●  A_m  =  archetypal  mode  
 ●  S_k  =  story  node  
 ●  E_j  =  energetic  modulation  
 ●  w_i  =  amplitude  weighting  
 
This  equation  parallels  quantum  superposition  but  applies  to  narrative  dynamics.
